We own the business.

00:45:56.972 --> 00:45:57.930
No one can take us out.

00:45:57.930 --> 00:45:59.800
We don't have to worry
about reported income.

00:45:59.800 --> 00:46:01.549
Why don't we go in and
see what we can do?

00:46:01.549 --> 00:46:05.130
Now since then, obviously,
