00:50:53.100 --> 00:50:56.030
control, which is the
alignment of interest

00:50:56.030 --> 00:50:59.740
for the long term, which means
that they're often treated more

00:50:59.740 --> 00:51:01.760
cheaply in the
marketplace because people

00:51:01.760 --> 00:51:04.290
worry about corrupt families.

00:51:04.290 --> 00:51:09.260
But the irony is that instead
of celebrating family control,

00:51:09.260 --> 00:51:11.440
in their proxy
statement, they have

00:51:11.440 --> 00:51:15.271
to have a section that
says, "A risk factor is

00:51:15.271 --> 00:51:17.020
a substantial majority
of our voting stock

