is controlled by members
of the Brown family,

00:51:18.700 --> 00:51:20.283
and collectively
they have the ability

00:51:20.283 --> 00:51:23.240
to control the outcome of
shareholder votes including

00:51:23.240 --> 00:51:23.884
this and that.

00:51:23.884 --> 00:51:25.300
We believe that
having a long-term

00:51:25.300 --> 00:51:27.900
focused commitment and engaged
shareholder base provides us

00:51:27.900 --> 00:51:31.290
the important strategic
advantage, so on and so forth."

00:51:31.290 --> 00:51:34.810
However, they flag
it as a risk factor.

