00:59:02.100 --> 00:59:05.030
that his job was to deliver
to his successor a much

00:59:05.030 --> 00:59:05.880
stronger company.

00:59:05.880 --> 00:59:07.230
That's his view.

00:59:07.230 --> 00:59:10.450
And so every year since
he's been at the helm,

00:59:10.450 --> 00:59:12.720
the gross dollar
volume of business,

00:59:12.720 --> 00:59:15.920
pass-through of their business,
is growing about 13% a year.

00:59:15.920 --> 00:59:18.000
It's a very high
fixed-cost business,

00:59:18.000 --> 00:59:21.390
so all that advance
