And so they poured back into
the business investments

00:59:47.885 --> 00:59:49.260
against the income
statement that

00:59:49.260 --> 00:59:52.660
keeps the income
statement low, lower

00:59:52.660 --> 00:59:57.400
than it would be if they
just let those advances.

00:59:57.400 --> 01:00:02.220
Now, the trick is, they have
partners in this business.

01:00:02.220 --> 01:00:04.510
They have partners in
the form of governments.

01:00:04.510 --> 01:00:06.860
And n Africa, for
example, the government

01:00:06.860 --> 01:00:09.540
